                            <comment id="41130" author="robert.kasanicky" created="Thu, 13 Nov 2008 23:21:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There seem to be 2 ways to go:&lt;br/&gt;
1. Document the current behavior properly and consider it a feature rather than bug&lt;br/&gt;
